  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK910">
<l>eṇcērnta neñcat tiṭaṉuṭaiyārk keññāṉṟum</l>
<l> peṇcērntām pētaimai yil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The foolishness that results from devotion to a wife will never be found in those who possess a reflecting mind and a prosperity (flowing) therefrom.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
